Overview
--------

Release 3.11.7 is the 8th release in
the Errata Tool 3.11 development period. It closes [21 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

The highlights of this release include improved support for multi-product
errata, enhancements related to TPS scheduling and troubleshooting, and a new
mechanism for setting "reboot suggested".

